I'm studying.

116
00:07:30,574 --> 00:07:31,617
Hello.

117
00:07:31,742 --> 00:07:32,952
Hello, ma'am.

118
00:07:34,620 --> 00:07:36,497
I'll be right there.

119
00:07:38,290 --> 00:07:41,502
I don't know how much you know.

120
00:07:41,627 --> 00:07:46,131
The work is taking care of my father.

121
00:07:46,256 --> 00:07:48,300
There is some housework too,

122
00:07:48,425 --> 00:07:52,388
but the main work is giving him
his medication on time,

123
00:07:52,513 --> 00:07:57,184
keeping him away from the stove,
from leaving the house.

124
00:07:57,309 --> 00:08:00,270
Termeh, get your laundry.

125
00:08:00,396 --> 00:08:05,317
You have to be here at 7:30
so I can go to work.

126
00:08:05,901 --> 00:08:07,820
