Ring the upstairs bell.

132
00:08:20,457 --> 00:08:23,669
I'll leave the house keys up here.

133
00:08:23,794 --> 00:08:24,920
- OK?
- Yes.

134
00:08:25,045 --> 00:08:27,297
Can you pay us please?

135
00:08:27,423 --> 00:08:29,091
What's the pay per month?

136
00:08:29,216 --> 00:08:30,509
She'll be right there.

137
00:08:30,634 --> 00:08:31,802
300,000 a month.

138
00:08:31,927 --> 00:08:33,554
That's too little.

139
00:08:33,679 --> 00:08:35,472
No, that's the rate.

140
00:08:35,597 --> 00:08:37,391
