The commute is far.

141
00:08:37,516 --> 00:08:39,309
Several bus lines.

142
00:08:39,435 --> 00:08:41,145
It's what I can afford.

143
00:08:41,270 --> 00:08:44,481
If you agree
you can start tomorrow.

144
00:08:44,606 --> 00:08:45,899
Can I let you know tomorrow?

145
00:08:46,025 --> 00:08:48,277
They might need this too.

146
00:08:48,402 --> 00:08:49,570
