- Come on.

181
00:11:29,396 --> 00:11:31,982
Don't put your hand there.

182
00:11:59,134 --> 00:12:00,594
I'm taking this CD.

183
00:12:02,095 --> 00:12:03,430
Take whichever you want.

184
00:12:03,555 --> 00:12:05,432
No, just this one.

185
00:12:23,784 --> 00:12:24,826
Bye.

186
00:12:58,026 --> 00:13:01,488
I thought you live there too.

187
00:13:02,281 --> 00:13:03,991
